Class Summary
AddressType The AddressType object define the types of addresses for a user to access the data from security xmls.
EmailType The EmailType object define the types of email address for a user to access the data from security xmls.
Permissions The Permission object define the Permissions a user can have to access the data from security xmls.
SecurityObject The SecurityObject object define all the objects for which security applies.
User The User object defines all the user in security.
UserAddress The UserAddress object define the all the addresses for a user in security xmls.
UserDateStamp  
UserEmail The UserEmail object stores all the email addresses for a user in security.
UserGroup The UserGroup object define the UserGroups for security.
UserSecurityObjectMapping The UserSecurityObjectMapping object ties User to the SecurityObjects for which security applies.
WebServiceMapping The WebServiceMapping object defines all the security applied to Webservice scenarios.
